job.description:
We are looking for skilled developers or an agency with expertise in Healthcare, HIPAA, Telemedicine, AI integrations, and EHR/EMR.

The project is a cutting-edge SaaS platform for medical providers and patients. The core features include repeat prescriptions, doctor appointment booking, electronic medical record (EMR) management, and comprehensive dashboards for users and healthcare providers, AI integrations.

Functionality and requirements:
- Catering to over 10,000 active users;
- Patients portal;
- Document Management;
- Billing and Invoicing;
- History (audit);
- Video Calling and Messaging;
- Tele-consultation Scheduling;
- Strict adherence to Healthcare regulations such as HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act) and GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation), WCAG 2.1;
- Appointment scheduling;
- Sending E-Mail directly from the app;
- Sending SMS from the software;
- Integrations (Calendar Support. EHR/EMR, Medical Billing, Medical Scheduling, Multi-PACS Software, Pharmacies Support, and Video Communications);
- Hardware Requirements (Mobile Cart Systems, Wall-mounted Access Point of Care Systems, Remote Monitoring Devices, Webcam, Wearable Devices, On-site Kiosk.

Functionality planned for later:
- AI Health Services;
- Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM);
- Medical Research;
- Migrating function: from other software: all data, documents, Laboratory value, etc.;
- Internal E-Mail system.

